entries.m_sorry: May the Force be with you.
entries.m_betrayed: I'm disappointed. I thought you looked like someone who didn't kowtow to the Empire.
entries.m_saved: I'm certain they would have tried to get information out of me about the Alliance. You've probably saved more than just my life here today. Thanks!
entries.a_tired_waiting: You have been warned. Take him down!
entries.a_thank_negotiate_again: The situation is clear. Heading back to base.
entries.a_negotiate_fail: That's enough. Our commander will do the interrogation back at base.
entries.a_waiting: This is your last chance. Come with us now, or we will take you in by force.
entries.a_greet_mad: Halt! Come with us for questioning now or we'll shoot.
entries.minion_3: There are more traitors to round up.
entries.a_thank_negotiate: Thank you for your assistance in this matter.
entries.a_thank_combat: The rebel shouldn't have resisted. You've served the Empire well.
entries.a_respond_m_1: We will ascertain that back at base. Come with us.
entries.m_greet_a: Who? Me? What did I do? I think you have the wrong person.
entries.a_greet_m: Halt! Come with us peacefully. You are wanted for questioning.
entries.m_waiting: Be careful, I think I can hear them coming.
entries.m_thank_negotiate: Whew, thanks. The rebellion owes you a debt of gratitude for this.
entries.response_negotiate: Wait. This isn't the suspect you are looking for.
entries.a_accept_offer: He was with you? All right, we're going to let him go for now, but he better not try to leave the planet.
entries.a_decline_offer: I asked for evidence, not an alibi. He's coming with us now.
entries.m_no_negotiate: I knew I should have checked the room for hidden transmitters. Well, there's no easy way out of this one.
entries.m_will_negotiate: Couldn't have been me, because I was with you two hours ago. Isn't that right? Please.
entries.a_maybe: Not the right suspect? He was seen talking with known rebel sympathizers two hours ago. Does he have any evidence to say otherwise?
entries.a_no: You are in direct violation of an Imperial order and are under arrest.
entries.m_maybe: I don't think they have a positive ID on me. If you tell them I'm not a Rebel that may be enough to buy me time to get off this planet.
entries.a_greet_imperial: Stand aside. This is a known traitor. We can handle this situation.
entries.a_greet_rebel: Stand aside, unless you want to be arrested too.
entries.m_thank_combat: You probably saved my life there. The rebellion owes you a debt of gratitude for this.
entries.m_no: I'll be sent to an Imperial prison for sure. You know someday you've got to stick your neck out against the Empire. It is just going to get worse.
entries.m_yes: You don't like the Empire much either, eh? Great! When I distract them, you hit them. With your help, I can take them.
entries.a_greet: Stand aside. We're on official business to apprehend an enemy of the Empire.
entries.m_greet: Please help me. Imperial Stormtroopers are after me. They think I'm with the Rebellion. Can I get you to help me out here?
